On Jan 16, 2020, at 9:48 PM, wrote:
> Hi - I assume, given the news coverage, that your team and the executives have seen the lawsuit filed by 
the Virgin Islands government against Epstein's estate, the 1953 Trust, and various entities (which seeks, among 
other relief, to void the fraudulent transfer of assets to the trust)? If not, let me know and I can circulate the 
complaint and more detail to the broader group. 
EFTA00018099
